<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us - Budgetbites</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .main-content {
      flex: 1;
      padding-right: 20px;
    }

    .section-container {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .section-container h1, .section-container h2 {
      text-align: center;
    }

    figure {
      width: 50%;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .story-container {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 100%;
    }

    .team-container {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 300px;
    }

    .team-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .team-list {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .team-list li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    strong {
      color: #fca94d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="main-content">
        <h1>Welcome to <strong>BudgetBites!</strong></h1>
        <p>Click "Home" to log in or make an account, or click "Search" to search for recipes now!</p>
      </section>
      <section class="section-container">

      <figure class="food-image">
      <img src="/images/instanramen.jpg" alt="Team Photo" />
    </figure>
      <section class="story-container" id="story">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>We're a group of broke college students who wanted to make cooking easier and more affordable for ourselves and our peers. Faced with the challenge of finding cheap and tasty recipes online, we decided to take matters into our own hands.</p>
        <p>With a shared passion for good food and a tight budget, we created Budget Bites. Our website is a hub for simple, wallet-friendly recipes tailored to the college lifestyle. From quick microwave meals to easy one-pot wonders, we've gathered recipes that anyone can make without breaking the bank.</p>
        <p>Our goal is to help students eat well without spending a fortune. Join us on our mission to make cooking accessible and enjoyable for everyone. Welcome to Budget Bites, where tasty meals meet tight budgets!</p>
      </section>
    </div>
    <aside class="team-container">
      <h2 class="team-title">Meet the Team</h2>
      <ul class="team-list">
        <li>Donny</li>
        <li>Vanessa Senethong</li>
        <li>Ima</li>
        <li>Alex</li>
        <li>Owen</li>
        <li>Johnny</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</body>
</html>